&lt;p data-start=&quot;1426&quot; data-end=&quot;1716&quot;&gt;This role requires strong technical fluency, disciplined project management, and the ability to drive alignment across customers, internal teams, and third-party integrators. You will play a key role in ensuring deployments run smoothly and consistently as Formic scales its robotics fleet.&lt;/p&gt;
